article_id:3059,category_name:News,title_name:A Sigil Spotlight Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>A Sigil Spotlight summon showcase starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1662098400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">In this summon showcase, players may exchange wyrmsigils for any of the 5★ adventurers or dragons who are eligible to appear. For further information, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu while this showcase is available, then tap the Wyrmsigils button for this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1662098400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1663307999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers and dragons eligible to appear in this showcase below.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ adventurers:</div><div>
